        <li style="padding: 10px 0;"><strong>Social media sellers are the primary counterfeit channel</strong> — never buy nicotine pouches from Instagram, Telegram, or Facebook Marketplace.</li>
        <li style="padding: 10px 0;"><strong>Buy from authorised retailers</strong> listed on the brand's official website, or from established specialist shops with verifiable business registration.</li>
